OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cold with a mix of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and frequent showers which will
OL,7,Fbe heavy at times with a risk of hail
OL,8,Fand thunder. Breezy near western
OL,9,Fcoasts with occasionally strong
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly winds, winds lighter in
OL,11,Feast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,14,Fclear spells, with showers easing and
OL,15,Fbecoming increasingly confined to
OL,16,Fcoastal parts. Touch of frost possible
OL,17,Fin sheltered spots, but breezy near
OL,18,Fwest coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
