OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FMainly dry start with sunny
OL,6,Fspells but occasionally heavy showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping widely through the morning,
OL,8,Fbefore easing in the west later.
OL,9,FNortherly winds, occasionally strong
OL,10,Fnear coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry with sunny spells through Friday
OL,14,Fand Saturday, risk of overnight
OL,15,Ffrosts. Outbreaks of rain in west
OL,16,FSunday morning edge east before
OL,17,Fclearing from west in afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
